    "script": "A: Did you arrange your project?\nB: Yes, I attend classes regularly.\nA: What is your purpose?\nB: To achieve success.\nA: That sounds good.\nB: I follow a theory of hard work.\nA: Can you explain?\nB: Balance study and rest.\nA: Did you face challenges?\nB: Yes, they were huge.\nA: How did you handle it?\nB: My teacher encouraged me.\nA: Will you present it?\nB: Yes, I will announce it tomorrow.\nA: Good luck!\nB: Thank you.",
